{"tid":1681871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"831後前綫消防員心聲","createTime":"2019-10-29T16:44:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T17:19:19.000Z","uid":274161,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ece411b38b981b8ce84627d00aedd09c2c42bc59","tid":1681871,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L2_UoD6LYRQ&amp;list=PLjcaikhnoRbMjrADCQd4SQ2OkZKyTaov3&amp;index=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DL2_UoD6LYRQ%26list%3DPLjcaikhnoRbMjrADCQd4SQ2OkZKyTaov3%26index%3D2&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2BsgzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=e86ac837\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L2_UoD6LYRQ&amp;list=PLjcaikhnoRbMjrADCQd4SQ2OkZKyTaov3&amp;index=2</a><br />\n<br />\n反修例運動至今已經四個月，香港人於這場運動都有不同的角色。阿呆（化名）是一名消防員。一穿上了一套黃金戰衣，他都秉持着「救火救人」的原則，不管政見與顏色。<br />\n<br />\n在示威現場，每當有人被困，有雜物燃燒，有人生命受威脅，都會看見他（或他的同僚）勇猛的身影。人心肉造，四個月來，他感觸良多。<br />\n<br />\n831之後，各種衝突及武力都漸趨白熱化，包括警察與消防之間，微妙的角力。消防處調配泵車協助警察工作。消防員被命令清理路障。他，作為民望最高紀律部隊的前線一員，有感被警隊「拉落水」，感到不滿，敢怒不敢言。<br />\n<br />\n阿呆尤其對831警方的處理手法感到憤怒，認為這件事與消防員「救急扶危」的宗旨有衝突。所以作為和理非的他，願意踏出一步，參與義載，駕駛着「校巴」，接載「仔仔女女」安全回家，沒有子女的他是這樣形容。<br />\n<br />\n他眼神堅定地說：「我有些同事，在社交媒體發表了一些言論，被上司『照肺』。我不怕這些壓力，因為我不是在做錯的事。如果我也怕，我怎樣對得住前線在衝的小朋友？」<br />\n<br />\n訪問間，談831，談「火魔法」，該義載。他做的事，彷彿也是每個人可以做的事。"},{"pid":"fb8763a370e37ebf9a319757937074e9009ba331","tid":1681871,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:44:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ee119048cf73350b4ac95ba0c6972a28e2f48d61","tid":1681871,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"【和你Thank】感謝前線消防活動  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#ThankYouHKFirefighters<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651243</a>"},{"pid":"9449f062eb25a64894205ea6a7104269477aa565","tid":1681871,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"MPWeekly明周有一個抗爭時代的play list，有40幾條片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1EhfSv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX1EhfSv.png&h=59507bc9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ad49de76f3cacaac1fe4402d200a65d1b3bfbe4","tid":1681871,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee119048cf73350b4ac95ba0c6972a28e2f48d61","tid":1681871,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"【和你Thank】感謝前線消防活動  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#ThankYouHKFirefighters<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651243</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"你個回復好應我個主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9deb2a18ecb30b53f575bca0a87fd01663e433","tid":1681871,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ad49de76f3cacaac1fe4402d200a65d1b3bfbe4","tid":1681871,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee119048cf73350b4ac95ba0c6972a28e2f48d61","tid":1681871,"uid":299387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:45:18.000Z","msg":"【和你Thank】感謝前線消防活動  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#ThankYouHKFirefighters<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1651243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1651243</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"你個回復好應我個主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:51:42.000Z","msg":"有比較就有傷害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899c48209a00212650cd02ff0e3ed402a9049